---
---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="container about__inner">
    <div class="about__left">
      <p class="about__label mono accent">→ About</p>
      <h2 class="about__title">
        I don't teach<br>
        <em>what I haven't</em><br>
        done myself.
      </h2>
      <div class="about__divider"></div>
      <p class="about__text">
        I built the world's largest cycling brand database from scratch — 15,000 stores, 
        zero budget, pure systems thinking. While training for a 1,500km raid across 
        multiple countries.
      </p>
      <p class="about__text">
        Everything I share is field-tested. The Big Ass Calendar isn't theory — it's 
        how I run 5 active projects while logging serious kilometers in the saddle. 
        The AI templates aren't demos — they're the actual pipelines generating leads 
        while I sleep.
      </p>
      <p class="about__text">
        My philosophy is simple: <strong>systems compound</strong>. The right structure 
        in your business or your life creates leverage that turns average effort into 
        extraordinary results.
      </p>
      <div class="about__tags">
        <span class="about__tag">Logotherapy</span>
        <span class="about__tag">Active Nihilism</span>
        <span class="about__tag">Agentic AI</span>
        <span class="about__tag">We Ride For Smiles</span>
        <span class="about__tag">Stoicism</span>
        <span class="about__tag">Deep Work</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about__right">
      <div class="about__card">
        <div class="about__card-header">
          <span class="mono" style="font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:var(--gray-400);text-transform:uppercase;">Current stack</span>
        </div>
        <div class="about__stack">
          <div class="about__stack-item">
            <span class="about__stack-dot"></span>
            <div>
              <div class="about__stack-name">The Bike Database</div>
              <div class="about__stack-desc">15K global cycling stores</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="about__stack-item">
            <span class="about__stack-dot"></span>
            <div>
              <div class="about__stack-name">We Ride For Smiles</div>
              <div class="about__stack-desc">Charity ultra-cycling raid</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="about__stack-item">
            <span class="about__stack-dot"></span>
            <div>
              <div class="about__stack-name">AI Lead Gen Templates</div>
              <div class="about__stack-desc">Agentic scraping systems</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="about__stack-item">
            <span class="about__stack-dot"></span>
            <div>
              <div class="about__stack-name">Systems Masterclass</div>
              <div class="about__stack-desc">Business OS course</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="about__stack-item">
            <span class="about__stack-dot"></span>
            <div>
              <div class="about__stack-name">Kikiyomi Method</div>
              <div class="about__stack-desc">Language immersion system</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about__proof">
        <div class="about__proof-item">
          <div class="about__proof-line"></div>
          <p class="mono" style="font-size:0.7rem;color:var(--gray-400);letter-spacing:0.08em;">
            "The only way to do great work is to build the infrastructure that makes great work inevitable."
          </p>
          <span class="mono" style="font-size:0.65rem;color:var(--accent);">— BM</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.about {
  padding: var(--section-pad) 0;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
}

.about__inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: clamp(40px, 6vw, 100px);
  align-items: start;
}

.about__label {
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.about__title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5vw, 5rem);
  line-height: 0.92;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.about__title em {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--accent);
}

.about__divider {
  width: 48px;
  height: 2px;
  background: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  transform-origin: left;
  animation: slideRight 0.8s 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) both;
}

.about__text {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: var(--gray-300);
  line-height: 1.75;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.about__text strong {
  color: var(--white);
  font-weight: 500;
}

.about__tags {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 8px;
  margin-top: 32px;
}

.about__tag {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 5px 12px;
  border: 1px solid var(--gray-700);
  color: var(--gray-400);
}

.about__card {
  background: var(--gray-900);
  border: 1px solid var(--gray-700);
  padding: 32px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.about__card-header {
  padding-bottom: 20px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.about__stack {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 20px;
}

.about__stack-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 14px;
}

.about__stack-dot {
  width: 6px;
  height: 6px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--accent);
  margin-top: 6px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.about__stack-name {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--white);
  font-weight: 400;
  margin-bottom: 2px;
}

.about__stack-desc {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  color: var(--gray-400);
}

.about__proof {
  padding: 24px;
  border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
  background: var(--gray-900);
}

.about__proof-item {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 12px;
}

.about__proof-line {
  width: 20px;
  height: 1px;
  background: var(--accent);
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .about__inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
